===Provincial & municipal government===
The party held several seats in [[Gemeenteraad|municipal legislatives]] and in the [[Noord Holland]] [[Provinciale Staten|Provincial legislative]].

==Electorate==
The CDP had only a limited support, which it drew Protestants from lower classes.

